01:11:44.250 --> 01:11:45.250
Bapak pulang.

01:11:46.041 --> 01:11:47.208
Bapak.

01:11:48.083 --> 01:11:48.916
Oi.

01:11:49.666 --> 01:11:50.666
Di rumah saja kalian?

01:11:55.500 --> 01:11:56.458
Ya, Sayang.

01:11:58.791 --> 01:12:00.833
Kenapa mukamu begitu?

01:12:05.000 --> 01:12:07.208
Pak, tadi Opung ke sini.

01:12:08.750 --> 01:12:10.875
Opung pasti rindu kepadamu, Nak.

01:12:10.958 --> 01:12:12.291
