01:16:31.666 --> 01:16:35.625
Padahal aku cuma korban. Divide et impera.

01:16:38.166 --> 01:16:39.166
Selamat tinggal, Madam.

01:16:40.208 --> 01:16:42.041
Selamat tinggal, Istana Kodok.

01:16:43.083 --> 01:16:44.791
