01:17:53.833 --> 01:17:55.958
Selamat ulang tahun, Suamiku.

01:17:57.541 --> 01:17:58.916
Pasienku.

01:18:03.083 --> 01:18:04.250
Rajaku.

01:18:07.625 --> 01:18:08.708
[dengkuran]

01:18:11.625 --> 01:18:14.166
Semoga kau panjang umur, Bang.

01:18:18.375 --> 01:18:21.375
Aku tidak bisa hidup tanpa Abang.

01:18:23.458 --> 01:18:25.166
Selalu sehat, Bang.

01:18:48.833 --> 01:18:51.875
[getar ponsel]

01:19:05.041 --> 01:19:06.791
- Raja.
- Ya, Bu.

01:19:07.916 --> 01:19:09.500
Bagaimana kau ini?

01:19:10.416 --> 01:19:11.375
Kau lupa hari ini?

01:19:12.250 --> 01:19:13.416
