01:24:34.916 --> 01:24:37.416
Dokter, bangunkan anakku.

01:24:38.125 --> 01:24:39.583
Hidupkan dia.

01:24:40.125 --> 01:24:42.125
Aku kasih semua hartaku.

01:24:43.375 --> 01:24:44.291
Kami mohon maaf, Bu.

01:24:46.083 --> 01:24:48.166
Bapak, bangun.

01:24:48.875 --> 01:24:51.416
Jangan meninggalkan Nico.

01:24:51.958 --> 01:24:53.958
Bapak.

01:24:54.416 --> 01:24:57.375
Bangun, Anakku. Bangun!

01:24:58.791 --> 01:25:01.208
Bangun, anak Ibu yang Ibu sayang.

